{
  "stem": "15396.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- You know, I-- I hate to tell you, but in those days, the curriculum for young students and all was lacking an awful lot in-- in the really important things, especially historical things and things of this sort.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I knew, somewhat, and I knew that they had been persecuted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- one time, we had a little run in with a couple of friends of ours about something to do with this, about this particular teacher.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was a definite anti-Semitic remark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't realize it was quite what it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't know the significance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But all I thought was that he was criticizing my friend.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't realize that it was a definite anti-Semitic remark.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Abe Wolf Davidson.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, he was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did in-- later on, when I went-- I went to Washington for a while, and for some reason, I was accepted in a fraternity house.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wasn't in school there, I was-- that time, I was wrestling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember taking a Jewish girl to one of their dances and there were no Jewish members of the fraternity and I never understood why.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I'm positive they weren't anti-Semitic, because this girl was the most popular girl, I think, at the dance, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'd-- I don't think we ever ran into that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe it's because, you know, I would have reacted in such a way, I guess, that, that people wouldn't bring it up with me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I never saw much evidence of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I did in Paris--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--later on, as a student.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I was about 18, I think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I studied under-- I studied under a man name, named [INAUDIBLE], and I thought he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
